    "_comment_design": "DISCOM publishes per-EnergyResource telemetry that originated from the aggregator's vendor-API integrations (e.g. Tata EVP Telematics, MG iMotion \u2014 collected out-of-band) AFTER actuals and BEFORE settlement. This is a non-settlement-grade reconciliation channel only \u2014 settlement is computed by the meter-based revenue rego against utility-published grid-meter BASELINE/USAGE in the actuals message, never against this EnergyResource data. BASELINE is deliberately absent here because baselines are exclusively utility-provided. PER_INTERVAL payloads (USAGE/POWER/SOC_END) appear in every interval; PER_EVENT payloads (GPS_LAT/GPS_LON) appear only on interval 0.",
